quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Say: \"O you people who reject Faith"
  109,2,I do not worship what you worship
  109,3,Nor will you worship what I worship
  109,4,And I will not worship what you have been used to worship
  109,5,Nor will you worship what I worship
  109,6,"To you be your religion, and to me (be) my religion"